0.1.0.name: connect20/Zenprint_Store_Price
0.1.0.description: This is a simple package that allows product prices to be set at the store level instead of just at the default and website levels. This allows for more flexible usage of store configurations.

suggest.magento-hackathon\/magento-composer-inst: Allows to manage this package as a dependency
